WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD
   TOWING 12 7000 METER LONG CABLES:
   A. IN PROGRESS UNTIL 21 MAR ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
      34-50.07S 052-34.47W AND 35-30.08S 051-32.05W.
   B. 21 AND 22 MAR ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
      35-24.22S 051-29.18W AND 34-44.20S 052-31.58W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 23 MAR 13.
